Package aima.core.search.framework.qsearch Description

This package contains different queue search implementations and a common interface for them, which is implicitly defined by abstract class QueueSearch. Given a problem and a non-empty queue of nodes (which is defined and initialized by some search strategy), the implementations control search space exploration and return a non-empty list of actions if a goal state was found.
Author:
Ruediger Lunde
